---
// 获取当前年份，用于底部版权声明自动更新
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-white border-t-2 border-wata-lightPink mt-12 pb-8 pt-10 sm:pt-16">
  <div class="max-w-[1600px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
      
      <div class="md:col-span-5 lg:col-span-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-5">
          <img src="/favicon.svg" alt="biliVManga" class="w-8 h-8 sm:w-10 sm:h-10" />
          <span class="text-xl font-black title-font text-wata-dark tracking-tight">
            biliVManga
          </span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed max-w-md">
          小站为一个非盈利性质的有声漫画汉化作品索引导航站，
          我们不提供任何视频上传或存储服务。所有引用的视频封面、标题及链接内容，其版权均归属于有声漫画原作者。
        </p>
        <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed max-w-md mt-2">
          统计数据均由UP主 <a href="https://space.bilibili.com/1764312492" target="_blank" class="flex items-left text-xs sm:text-sm font-bold text-gray-500 hover:text-wata-pink transition-colors no-underline hover:underline decoration-2 underline-offset-4">敔信 <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="ml-1" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" strokeWidth="2.5" strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round"><path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"/><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"/><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"/></svg></a> 收集并授权。<br>
          网站由 MqyGalaxy 制作，如有争议内容，请通过“联系小站”进行协商或联系删除。
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-7 lg:col-span-6 grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xs font-black text-wata-purple tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">导航</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li><a href="/" class="text-xs sm:text-sm font-bold text-gray-500 hover:text-wata-pink transition-colors">首页</a></li>
            <li><a href="/about/" class="text-xs sm:text-sm font-bold text-gray-500 hover:text-wata-pink transition-colors">关于小站</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xs font-black text-wata-purple tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">帮助</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li><a href="/faq/" class="text-xs sm:text-sm font-bold text-gray-500 hover:text-wata-pink transition-colors">常见问题</a></li>
            <li><a href="/connect/" class="text-xs sm:text-sm font-bold text-gray-500 hover:text-wata-pink transition-colors">联系小站</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="col-span-2 sm:col-span-1">
          <h3 class="text-xs font-black text-wata-purple tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">链接</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li><a href="https://www.kdocs.cn/l/csyFz3aAKxde" target="_blank" class="flex items-left text-xs sm:text-sm font-bold text-gray-500 hover:text-wata-pink transition-colors">表格更新 <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="ml-1" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" strokeWidth="2.5" strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round"><path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"/><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"/><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"/></svg></a></li>
            <li><a href="https://github.com/MqyGalaxy/biliVManga" target="_blank" class="flex items-left text-xs sm:text-sm font-bold text-gray-500 hover:text-wata-pink transition-colors">GitHub <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="ml-1" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" strokeWidth="2.5" strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round"><path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"/><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"/><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"/></svg></a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="col-span-2 sm:col-span-1">
          <h3 class="text-xs font-black text-wata-purple tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">协议</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li><a href="https://www.moeqy.com/privacy/" target="_blank" class="flex items-left text-xs sm:text-sm font-bold text-gray-500 hover:text-wata-pink transition-colors">隐私协议 <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="ml-1" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" strokeWidth="2.5" strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round"><path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"/><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"/><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"/></svg></a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 sm:mt-12 pt-6 sm:pt-8 border-t border-gray-100 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4">
      <p class="text-[11px] sm:text-xs font-bold text-gray-400">
        &copy; {currentYear} biliVManga. Some rights reserved.
      </p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[11px] sm:text-xs font-bold text-gray-400">
        <span>由所有 <span class="text-wata-pink animate-pulse inline-block">❤</span> 有声漫画的人共同制作</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>